description: InfinityLab Poroshell 120 is suitable for reversed-phase liquid chromatography separation provide excellent efficiency and reliability. Eleven chemically bonded phases (from C18 columns to unique chemically bonded phases) have up to three particle sizes: 1.9 µm, 2.7 µm, and 4 µm. This series of chemically bonded phases provides a wide range of selectivity for scalable liquid chromatography method development, from traditional HPLC to UHPLC to ultra-low diffusion UHPLC.
name: InfinityLab Poroshell 120
